# 🍰 Dolcino – Dessert & Cafe Website

**Dolcino** is a visually appealing, static website project designed for a dessert or cafe brand. It is built using pure HTML and CSS, showcasing a clean, responsive layout suitable for portfolio or client demonstrations.

---

## 📌 Project Overview

The website includes:

- A modern landing page
- About and Menu sections
- Gallery and Testimonials
- Contact form (front-end only)
- Responsive design with mobile-friendly layout

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

| Technology     | Description                      |
|----------------|----------------------------------|
| HTML5          | Structure and semantic markup    |
| CSS3           | Styling and responsive layout    |
| Google Fonts   | Custom font styling              |
| Font Awesome   | Icons for features and social    |
